Mempersiapkan Tabel Project

Baik, berikut adalah beberapa perintah (command) MySQL yang penting dan wajib diketahui:

1. mysql -u root
2. SHOW DATABASES;
3. USE nama_database;
4. SHOW TABLES;
5. DESCRIBE kelas;
6. SHOW create table customers;
7. SHOW INDEX FROM items;

diagram entitas relasional (Entity-Relationship Diagram atau ERD).
ERD adalah diagram yang menggambarkan hubungan antar entitas dalam suatu sistem database.



=============================

1. CREATE TABLE `customers` (
  `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` char(50) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`ID`)
);

2. CREATE TABLE Products (
  ID int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  name char(50) NOT NULL,
  price decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (ID)
);

3. CREATE TABLE Orders (
  ID int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  customer_id int(11) NOT NULL,
  date timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp() ON UPDATE current_timestamp(),
  PRIMARY KEY (ID),
  key `CUSTOMER_ID` (`CUSTOMER_ID`),
  constraint `ORDER_IBFK_1` FOREIGN KEY (`customer_id`) REFERENCES `customers` (`ID`)
);


4. CREATE TABLE Items (
  ID int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  order_id int(11) NOT NULL,
  product_id int(11) NOT NULL,
  qty int NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (ID),
  KEY `fk_order_id` (`order_id`),
  KEY `fk_product_id` (`product_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_order_id` FOREIGN KEY (`order_id`) REFERENCES `Orders`(`ID`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_product_id` FOREIGN KEY (`product_id`) REFERENCES `Products`(`ID`)
);


=======================================
